  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria: adults living in the study catchment area (Gem Village, Nyanza province
        Western Kenya) served by one of 23 HIV clinics and 3 referral labs

          -  Not having received HIV care in prior 6 months if known HIV+

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  current HIV care or HIV care within last six months
      </textblock>
